version_description: The other versions are incomplete in chords and formatting.
Substitutions here, especially Em7 (intro and verse) and Am7 (verse refrain). Additional substitutions throughout. Option to tie high G through many of the changes.
From the Running On Empty album. Played live. Fairly simple to play. Great song. Enjoy.
G major borrows from G minor.
These are the chords used in the recording, but also can be used to replicate the acoustic version performed with David Crosby.
